      <tr><td>Hotend Kit (hotend + 4 silicone socks + 5 nozzles)</td><td><a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0F61P4TMJ" target="_blank">amazon.com/dp/B0F61P4TMJ</a></td></tr>
